---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Clement Hoang">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-normal tracking-tight text-ink mb-12 font-display">Clement Hoang</h1>

  <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink mb-16">
    <p>
      I'm a software engineer and builder, based in San Francisco. I currently work at
      <a href="https://airtable.com" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 hover:decoration-2 transition-all duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Airtable</a>,
      leading agentic product development &mdash; an MCP server now live in the ChatGPT app store and as an
      <a href="https://claude.com/connectors/airtable" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 hover:decoration-2 transition-all duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">official Claude connector</a>,
      <a href="https://blog.airtable.com/superagent/" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 hover:decoration-2 transition-all duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Superagent</a>
      (an AI research agent), and an integrations platform connecting agents to hundreds of external services.
      I've also led enterprise readiness efforts across sandboxing, admin controls, and governance.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before that, I was tech lead at Credit Karma, where I shipped consumer financial products to millions of users &mdash;
      identity monitoring, credit locking, and the
      <a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/90624513/world-changing-ideas-awards-2021-pandemic-response-finalists-and-honorable-mentions" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 hover:decoration-2 transition-all duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Relief Center</a>
      (a Fast Company World Changing Ideas finalist). At Meta, I contributed to React core and shipped
      <a href="https://legacy.reactjs.org/blog/2017/11/28/react-v16.2.0-fragment-support.html" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 hover:decoration-2 transition-all duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fragments in v16.2</a>
      &mdash; now one of the most widely used patterns in the ecosystem.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm fascinated by how AI is reshaping the way software gets built, how money moves, and how
      businesses operate. When I'm not shipping, I'm probably deep in a recipe that seemed reasonable
      at the time, or chasing shuttlecocks on the badminton court.
    </p>
    <p>
      Drop me a line at <a href="mailto:me@clemmy.ninja" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 hover:decoration-2 transition-all duration-150">me@clemmy.ninja</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <nav aria-label="Social links" class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted border-t border-surface pt-8">
    <a href="https://github.com/clemmy" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://ca.linkedin.com/in/clementhoang" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://twitter.com/c8hoang" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://medium.com/@clemmmy" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Writing</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="https://instagram.com/professor.pan" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cooking</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
    <a href="/coaching" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-150">Coaching</a>
  </nav>
</Base>
